Section 4. Section 37-3-405, MCA, is amended to read:
"37-3-405. Suspension of license or privilege for failure to report. The willful failure of any person,
organization, association, society, or health care facility to comply with 37-3-401, 37-3-402, or 37-3-403 is
grounds for suspension of any a license or privilege granted by the state of Montana. Upon such failure, the
The agency granting the license or privilege may, in its discretion, suspend the license or privilege for a period
